{
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "header"
      },
      "source": [
        "# DiffSinger Miadu Fine-tuning (Colab 斷點續訓 + 共用硬碟支持版)\n",
        "**特點**：\n",
        "- 支持「個人硬碟」或「共用雲端硬碟」\n",
        "- 每 500 步自動保存權重至雲端\n",
        "- 支持斷點續訓，斷線重新執行即可從上次位置繼續"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "config-header"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 第一步：配置雲端硬碟路徑"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "config-code"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from google.colab import drive\n",
        "drive.mount('/content/drive')\n",
        "\n",
        "# ======================== 配置區 ========================\n",
        "# 如果您使用個人硬碟，請保持預設：\n",
        "DRIVE_BASE = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/DiffSinger_Colab\"\n",
        "\n",
        "# 如果您使用「共用雲端硬碟」，請取消下行註解並填寫您的硬碟名稱：\n",
        "# DRIVE_BASE = \"/content/drive/Shareddrives/您的硬碟名稱/DiffSinger_Colab\"\n",
        "# ========================================================\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"| 目前使用的雲端路徑為: {DRIVE_BASE}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "step2-header"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 第二步：獲取代碼與環境配置"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "step2-code"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "%cd /content/\n",
        "!git clone https://github.com/shihte/DiffSinger-Miadu-Colab.git diffsinger-repo\n",
        "%cd diffsinger-repo\n",
        "\n",
        "# 安裝必要依賴\n",
        "!pip install parselmouth pyloudnorm webrtcvad pypinyin lightning-flash==0.7.0 pycwt pyworld scipy==1.9.1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "step3-header"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 第三步：建立安全連接 (軟連結至 Drive)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "step3-code"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "\n",
        "# 確保雲端目錄存在\n",
        "if not os.path.exists(DRIVE_BASE):\n",
        "    os.makedirs(DRIVE_BASE)\n",
        "\n",
        "CKPT_DRIVE = f\"{DRIVE_BASE}/checkpoints_finetune\"\n",
        "if not os.path.exists(CKPT_DRIVE):\n",
        "    os.makedirs(CKPT_DRIVE)\n",
        "\n",
        "# 建立軟連結\n",
        "!rm -rf checkpoints\n",
        "!ln -s \"{CKPT_DRIVE}\" checkpoints\n",
        "\n",
        "# 初始化目錄\n",
        "!mkdir -p data/binary\n",
        "\n",
        "# 搬運預訓練權重與二進位數據 (如果雲端已有則不會重複覆蓋)\n",
        "if not os.path.exists(\"checkpoints/1117_opencpop_ds1000_strict_pinyin\"):\n",
        "    print(\"| 正在從 Drive 獲取基礎權重...\")\n",
        "    !cp -r \"{DRIVE_BASE}/1117_opencpop_ds1000_strict_pinyin\" checkpoints/\n",
        "    !cp -r \"{DRIVE_BASE}/nsf_hifigan_44.1k_hop512_128bin_2024.02\" checkpoints/\n",
        "\n",
        "if not os.path.exists(\"data/binary/miadu_finetune\"):\n",
        "    print(\"| 正在搬運二進位數據...\")\n",
        "    !cp -r \"{DRIVE_BASE}/miadu_finetune\" data/binary/\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"| 環境就緒！所有訓練進度將實時同步至雲端硬碟。\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "step4-header"
      },
      "source": [
        "## 第四步：啟動訓練 (支持自動斷點續訓)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "step4-code"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "os.environ['PYTHONPATH'] = \".\"\n",
        "\n",
        "# 啟動微調任務\n",
        "!python tasks/run.py --config usr/configs/midi/e2e/miadu_finetune.yaml --exp_name miadu_finetune_v1"
      ]
    }
  ],\n",
